Cincinnati football fans can get their first behind the scenes look at their favorite team starting tonight at 10 p.m. on HBO. In its eighth season, Hard Knocks is a reality show about the strategy and personnel behind NFL teams and culture. This season&rsquo;s series will mark the second time HBO has featured the Bengals. 
